# Trade with Tayyab — Frontend Environment Configuration
#
# The frontend calls the backend through the `apiFetch` helper in
# src/lib/api.ts, which resolves the base URL as follows:
#
#   - Web build:    relative /api/... paths, rewritten to the backend by
#                   vercel.json (production) and the Vite dev proxy (local).
#   - Native app:   absolute production backend URL (Capacitor WebView has no
#                   server to resolve relative paths — this fixes the mobile
#                   "Login server link error").
#
# You normally do NOT need to set anything here. Set VITE_API_URL only to
# override the base URL for both web and native (e.g. a staging backend).
# VITE_API_URL=https://trade-with-tayyab-lms.onrender.com
